Before you start the Cybernode:

export USER_OPTS="-DIGRID_HOME=<where you have iGrid-Rio> -DiGrid.home=<where you have iGrid-Rio>"
copy Sorcer.groovy $RIO_HOME/config/platform/.
copy start-sorcer-web.groovy $RIO_HOME/config/.

Them run:

$RIO_HOME/bin/cybernode

In a different terminal (shell) run:

$RIO_HOME/bin/rio start sorcer-web

In another terminal (shell) run:

$RIO_HOME/bin/monitor

Then run:

$RIO_HOME/bin/rio-ui

Select "Deploy", navigate to where you have Arithmetic.groovy, select the file, and deploy it.
